            <p>The Scottish Ministers make the following Regulations in exercise of the powers conferred by section 153 of the Local Government <abbr title="et cetera" xml:lang="la">etc.</abbr> (Scotland) Act 1994<noteRef href="#f00001" class="footnote" marker="1"/> and all other powers enabling them to do so.</p>
         </formula>
